;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-0b9af703cc318b5c36414d2f0fa77e76_b.jpg\&quot; data-caption=\&quot;\&quot; data-size=\&quot;normal\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1500\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;1154\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;1500\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-0b9af703cc318b5c36414d2f0fa77e76_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;1500&#x27;%20height=&#x27;1154&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-caption=\&quot;\&quot; data-size=\&quot;normal\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1500\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;1154\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;1500\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-0b9af703cc318b5c36414d2f0fa77e76_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-0b9af703cc318b5c36414d2f0fa77e76_b.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;一个漂亮的小村庄，农田郁郁葱葱，房屋错落有致，街道上还有太阳能路灯，典型的纳西族建筑风格。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-60fb0fb8c08b3f5ebaee60d6bdc5805c_b.jpg\&quot; data-caption=\&quot;\&quot; data-size=\&quot;normal\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;3000\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;1917\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;3000\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-60fb0fb8c08b3f5ebaee60d6bdc5805c_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;3000&#x27;%20height=&#x27;1917&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-caption=\&quot;\&quot; data-size=\&quot;normal\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;3000\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;1917\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;3000\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-60fb0fb8c08b3f5ebaee60d6bdc5805c_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-60fb0fb8c08b3f5ebaee60d6bdc5805c_b.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;气温在15到20度左右，微风吹面十分惬意&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-3d3afae225b41acd4ef8bee3321f9d67_b.jpg\&quot; data-caption=\&quot;\&quot; data-size=\&quot;normal\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;3000\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;2054\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;3000\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3d3afae225b41acd4ef8bee3321f9d67_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;3000&#x27;%20height=&#x27;2054&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-caption=\&quot;\&quot; data-size=\&quot;normal\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;3000\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;2054\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;3000\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3d3afae225b41acd4ef8bee3321f9d67_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-3d3afae225b41acd4ef8bee3321f9d67_b.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;给MINI也留给影。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-7e5a37e46cf4907172408dc8162e2fe5_b.jpg\&quot; data-caption=\&quot;\&quot; data-size=\&quot;normal\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1500\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;1147\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;1500\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7e5a37e46cf4907172408dc8162e2fe5_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;1500&#x27;%20height=&#x27;1147&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-caption=\&quot;\&quot; data-size=\&quot;normal\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1500\&quot; data-rawheight=\